data.description: The cutest, coziest house has arrived on the market in Lynnfield! Located on the corner of Canterbury Lane, (with the driveway on Canterbury), this adorable 3 bedroom home is filled with warmth and charm. With a newer kitchen and a light, bright and airy feel throughout, the home lives and feels larger than it's square footage. The basement is heated and partially finished for a potential home office or bonus room. Updated kitchen features white shaker cabinets, beautiful white counters, and stainless appliances. The open dining area has two picture windows and gets great sunlight throughout the day. The adjacent living room also has two large picture windows, one overlooking the deep front porch and the other overlooking the side yard. The yard is large and newly fenced for your four-legged friends. Quite an opportunity to get into Lynnfield and enjoy the wonderful community, school system and convenient location. Open Houses Sat. 4/20 & Sun. 4/21 from 11-12:30.
